{"tid":1533640,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"POPO 記者會表現ON9指數評分","createTime":"2019-09-02T18:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T18:37:02.000Z","uid":195035,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fd29660ed33588b9ee9b9269d752860df798e065","tid":1533640,"uid":195035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:35:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">POPO 記者會表現評分 - </span><br />\n<br />\n5粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為最膠<br />\n1粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為最唔膠<br />\n由螢光幕右至左順序：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gYO5YcO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgYO5YcO.png&h=84b4abcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">ER ER SIR -</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n迴避警察子女係咪有警察護送返學並進入學校範圍，夠鐘就起身走人，非常無恥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UDJd66e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUDJd66e.png&h=6c2bbdd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">當黑SIR -</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺回答港台記者追問時, 答非所問, 人地係問7個傷者入面有幾多個係普通巿民, 佢就一直遊花園, 不斷強調拉左嗰啲係暴徒, 記者追問嗰陣, 仲要西面, 最後比記者迫到無路可退, 結果一句 &quot;仲未有相關資料&quot; 就當答左, 賤撚得佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mt0v9jY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMt0v9jY.png&h=b151c9ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">精靈SIR：</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔承認差佬打巿民, 多次答問題時HANG撚晒機, 柒態盡現, 個樣雖然似隻精靈, 但個人就柒到冇朋友, 口材亦係五人之中最差勁, 偏偏最撚高級係佢, 比條廢物騎撚住, 我估佢班靚都覺得好唔撚順氣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/25220rJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F25220rJ.png&h=fe228feb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">消防陳SIR：</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外表正氣, 肯講人話, 承認救援時間唔理想, 當選是日MVP<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hGDxDdu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhGDxDdu.png&h=52b36d95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">西裝SIR：</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n四條差佬入面, 算係比較肯正面回答問題嗰個, 中英文能力亦係最好嗰個, 不過佢話唔肯定車廂喊晒嗰對情侶係咪受傷, 就係擘大眼講大話, DLLM 發晒癲咁扑落去個頭度, 都可以冇受傷?"},{"pid":"09721747a56c1708bb53474ae3def1775c2c6e5c","tid":1533640,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:35:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd00d0d39ba6b2cb043648ef8edde975296de659","tid":1533640,"uid":135867,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:36:29.000Z","msg":"唔好搞呢啲評分<br />\n<br />\n冷處理<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得許sir"},{"pid":"aa6c8d97d5445e303ff26fcef00177dabc7e4cc2","tid":1533640,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:36:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b696f83cff9e9148bff0f01e8e594fdaed6d629","tid":1533640,"uid":259613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd00d0d39ba6b2cb043648ef8edde975296de659","tid":1533640,"uid":135867,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:36:29.000Z","msg":"唔好搞呢啲評分<br />\n<br />\n冷處理<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得許sir"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0